Comment: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:29.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty metres down. Forty-five to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.73,0:01:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}With half a body length's lead, Araki's in good form \Nas he comes up on the fifty metre turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wasn't this guy fencing a minute ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he swimming?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the modern pentathlon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Shooting, fencing, swimming, equestrian, \Nand running. Five events in all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.38,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Penta" means five.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The triathlon is swimming, cycling, and marathon, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I don't get is biathlon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in that one again?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Skiing and shooting.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's not to get?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In a triathlon, all the events \Nhave one general theme: speed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In the modern pentathlon, it's like \Nyou're fighting with your gun and your sword,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.48,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}and getting around the battlefield \Nby running, swimming, and horse-riding.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's kind of a bloody event \Nwhen you think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's easy to imagine.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I see what you mean. \NWith two events, you can do whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's a Winter Olympics event, \Nso you've got to keep skiing,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.20,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}but why not pair it with playing cards, \Nor Frisbee, or snuggling in the warmth?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want them to fall asleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.26,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}On Knight Scoop the other day, \Nthey combined shogi with boxing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, sounds hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.01,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.97,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you cut shooting from the biathlon, \Nthey're going to have to run to make up for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.01,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, if you try and fail to bring down a bear,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd better be ready to run.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being watched...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.62,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A bear's stalking us!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't there last episode!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who forgot to put the hina dolls away?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be cursed to spinsterhood!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell have you guys done?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you forget to put away the dolls...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're cursed to hypothermic doom!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die on a mountain somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's "to die an old bride".
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marry late? That's hardly any different!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never gonna get married, \N and freeze to death all alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't stand a snowball's chance in hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}C'mon, guys. Let's just think about it calmly over some tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go prepare some!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I knew we had some matcha powder here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed to be an *ld maid forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,M*ld maid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a real thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's her!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.05,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The M*ld Maid!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She really {\i1}does{\i0} exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This is just matcha powder!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Stay back before she infects \Nyou with spinsterhood!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O Gods, protect me from this horror!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into one of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our adorable Kigu's been possessed!
